  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t我大川普在接受知名的親共和黨右翼媒體FOX採訪時大肆稱讚維尼。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n連結在此：<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9hdHJ1cGFyL3N0YXR1cy8xNjQ1OTUzNjQzMjEwODUwMzA0\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/atrupar/status/1645953643210850304\">https://twitter.com/atrupar/status/1645953643210850304</a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n採訪者：How smart is he?(他有多聰明?)<br/>\n<br/>\r\n川普：Top of the line.(最頂尖的程度。)<br/>\n<br/>\r\n採訪者：？<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOGFhMjQ5YTk0NGQ2MzdiNDlhYWQwLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8aa249a944d637b49aad0.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8aa249a944d637b49aad0.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8aa249a944d637b49aad0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n川普：President Xi is a brilliant man.(習主席是個才華洋溢的男人。)<br/>\r\n　　　if you went all over Hollywood to look for somebody to play the role of President Xi you couldn't find him.(即使找遍整個好萊塢也找不到人能扮演習主席。)<br/>\r\n　　　There's nobody like that.The look, the brain, the whole thing.(那裡沒有人像他一樣。外貌、頭腦、一切。)<br/>\n<br/>\r\n採訪者：？？？<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOGYzODU1ZTRkYTQ5YjdjNGNlYWI4LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8f3855e4da49b7c4ceab8.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8f3855e4da49b7c4ceab8.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8f3855e4da49b7c4ceab8.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n同場加映：<br/>\r\n川普說沙烏地阿拉伯是「偉大的政權」：<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9hdHJ1cGFyL3N0YXR1cy8xNjQ1OTQ2ODY3NjU2ODI2ODgw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/atrupar/status/1645946867656826880\">https://twitter.com/atrupar/status/1645946867656826880</a><br/>\r\n川普說他對於在2017年下令空襲敘利亞時殺死俄國士兵一事感到悲傷：<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9hdHJ1cGFyL3N0YXR1cy8xNjQ1OTUyODM5ODU4OTEzMjgw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/atrupar/status/1645952839858913280\">https://twitter.com/atrupar/status/1645952839858913280</a><br/>\r\n川普說普丁「非常聰明」：<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9hdHJ1cGFyL3N0YXR1cy8xNjQ1OTU0MTE4NTUxMzIyNjI2\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://twitter.com/atrupar/status/1645954118551322626\">https://twitter.com/atrupar/status/1645954118551322626</a><br/>\r\n心得：這傢伙有種想法我毫不意外，但他居然直接在鏡頭前說出來可真是嚇死我了。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
